The '''Talamp Industrial Sector''', or '''Talamp District''', was one of the major sectors of [[Corint City]], the [[Planet/Legends|planetary]] [[Capital/Legends|capital]] of the [[Outer Rim Territories/Legends|Outer Rim]] world of [[Pirik]]. Containing the industrial and manufacturing heart of the [[City/Legends|city]], it was located fifteen [[Kilometer/Legends|kilometers]] from [[Uloitir Sea]].

